OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with some long
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine and light winds.
OL,7,FTurning cloudier through the afternoon
OL,8,Fas rain spreads eastwards, feeling
OL,9,Fchilly with winds freshening too.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain moving away east with
OL,12,Fsome clear spells developing for a
OL,13,Ftime, cloud and rain spreading east in
OL,14,Fthe early hours.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FA wet and windy start on
OL,17,FSunday but some drier and brighter
OL,18,Fconditions developing in the north for
OL,19,Fa time, further rain later, turning
OL,20,Fheavy at times, strong winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
